WEBVTT

00:25.690 --> 00:27.290
What are you thinking about?

00:27.640 --> 00:28.640
Nothing.

00:29.480 --> 00:31.830
Why do I smell something burning?

00:34.150 --> 00:35.240
My dish!

00:48.890 --> 00:50.170
Did something happen?

01:04.930 --> 01:07.530
Qianqian wants to invite you
to be her husband.

01:08.350 --> 01:09.230
What?

01:10.400 --> 01:13.039
She sees a good catch
and now she wants to snatch him away, huh?

01:13.039 --> 01:14.920
No, she means to "borrow" him.

01:15.590 --> 01:17.560
To drive away a customer
who's been harassing her.

01:17.560 --> 01:18.960
That won't work, either.

01:19.680 --> 01:21.310
Dear, why are you pulling me?

01:21.370 --> 01:22.700
If a woman wanted to borrow you from me,

01:22.700 --> 01:23.980
would you be okay with it?

01:23.980 --> 01:26.840
Well, if she were gentle,
I guess I wouldn't mind.

01:26.920 --> 01:29.070
Say that again! I dare you!

01:29.070 --> 01:30.710
What kind of reward did she offer

01:30.710 --> 01:32.680
that you'd sell me out just for
a few taels of silver?

01:32.680 --> 01:35.170
How could I possibly sell you out
for just a few taels?

01:35.170 --> 01:36.150
Yeah, exactly.

01:36.150 --> 01:38.080
A few taels do sound a bit too cheap.

01:38.390 --> 01:39.509
Thirty taels.

01:40.430 --> 01:41.690
-What?
-Thirty taels?

01:45.710 --> 01:48.710
Well, Changyu means well, after all.

01:49.070 --> 01:51.340
Yan Zheng, why don't you just help out?

01:51.509 --> 01:53.240
Think of it as doing a good deed.

01:53.479 --> 01:54.210
Hey, wait...

01:54.430 --> 01:55.740
What? Why "hey, wait?"

01:55.759 --> 01:57.200
If you could sell for even 3 or 5 taels,

01:57.200 --> 01:58.120
I'd agree immediately.

01:58.120 --> 01:58.680
You...

02:00.120 --> 02:00.760
Changning.

02:00.760 --> 02:02.540
Let's go. Let's ignore them.

02:03.350 --> 02:05.630
Turns out I'm worth even less than a pig.

02:05.710 --> 02:07.840
And how much do you think you're worth?

02:08.240 --> 02:09.910
Why don't you ask someone else?

02:09.910 --> 02:12.360
Like that... Lord Li or whatever.

02:12.910 --> 02:14.620
Well, he's not in Lin'an.

02:18.780 --> 02:20.710
Even if he were, I wouldn't ask him.

02:21.630 --> 02:23.260
I've got my own husband—

02:23.400 --> 02:24.870
why go to an outsider?

02:30.630 --> 02:32.240
Just help Qianqian out.

02:32.470 --> 02:33.530
It's just for 1 day.

02:33.910 --> 02:35.150
If her Yixiang Restaurant goes under,

02:35.150 --> 02:37.010
our business will suffer as well.

02:38.310 --> 02:39.680
That rice merchant surnamed Qi

02:39.680 --> 02:41.240
clings to her like a stubborn bandage.

02:41.240 --> 02:43.120
He's just impossible to get rid of.

02:43.120 --> 02:44.840
Harmless, but irritating.

02:46.190 --> 02:47.920
The rice merchant surnamed Qi?

02:49.490 --> 02:51.840
Who has he been associating with lately?

02:51.870 --> 02:55.270
It's said to be a rice merchant
from the Capital, surnamed Qi.

02:58.260 --> 02:59.170
Just for 1 day?

02:59.240 --> 03:00.080
Just for 1 day.

04:26.980 --> 04:32.450
[Pursuit of Jade]

04:32.530 --> 04:35.130
[Episode 13]

04:35.220 --> 04:37.740
[Welcome guests from far and wide]

04:46.870 --> 04:47.870
This way, please.

04:47.920 --> 04:48.630
Zheng.

04:49.950 --> 04:52.000
In this outfit, let alone
a restaurant manager—

04:52.000 --> 04:53.860
you could even pass for a marquis.

04:54.190 --> 04:56.070
Not bad. This way, please.

04:59.200 --> 05:01.120
I'm counting on you today.

05:03.150 --> 05:04.000
Rest assured.

05:04.440 --> 05:05.270
Changyu said

05:05.600 --> 05:07.460
you're her best friend in Lin'an.

05:08.090 --> 05:09.390
If she wants to help you,

05:09.390 --> 05:11.120
I'll do it without hesitation.

05:12.570 --> 05:13.210
This way.

05:14.470 --> 05:17.290
[Heaven-class]

05:18.770 --> 05:19.740
Mr. Qi.

05:24.110 --> 05:26.550
Manager Yu, are you feeling better?

05:28.370 --> 05:31.210
Mr. Qi, this is my husband, Yan Zheng.

05:51.370 --> 05:53.740
He's been away on business recently.

05:53.740 --> 05:55.100
He just returned to Lin'an today,

05:55.100 --> 05:56.300
and I brought him here specifically

05:56.300 --> 05:59.250
to thank you for supporting
our humble restaurant's business.

05:59.250 --> 06:00.130
Mr. Qi.

06:01.210 --> 06:02.410
Pleasure to meet you.

06:03.740 --> 06:05.540
So you're Manager Yu's husband.

06:06.180 --> 06:06.840
Naturally.

06:20.740 --> 06:23.250
Yan Zheng, have a good chat with Mr. Qi.

06:23.250 --> 06:25.180
I'll go prepare some food and wine.

06:31.210 --> 06:32.050
Mr. Qi.

06:33.060 --> 06:33.659
Please.

06:42.010 --> 06:43.550
When Master throws his cup as a signal,

06:43.550 --> 06:45.350
that's our cue to tie that guy up.

06:49.180 --> 06:51.740
I heard you came from the Capital, Mr. Qi.

06:52.370 --> 06:54.890
I wonder why you've come to
our tiny Lin'an Town

06:54.890 --> 06:56.130
for grain business?

06:59.740 --> 07:02.180
Mr. Yan, you're not a local here either.

07:02.620 --> 07:05.660
So why are you running a restaurant
here in Lin'an?

07:11.250 --> 07:12.890
My wife may not
have attended to things properly.

07:12.890 --> 07:14.420
Please bear with us, Mr. Qi.

07:15.130 --> 07:16.730
Next time there's business,

07:16.860 --> 07:18.390
please come straight to me.

07:21.060 --> 07:24.250
It's just I wonder how big a deal
you can handle, Mr. Yan.

07:27.900 --> 07:28.860
For example...

07:31.010 --> 07:32.690
200,000 piculs of grain.

07:51.250 --> 07:52.130
Pardon me.

07:55.010 --> 07:57.409
With our Yixiang Restaurant doing so well,

07:58.540 --> 08:01.940
it's inevitable that some jealous rivals

08:02.620 --> 08:04.080
cause trouble in the dark.

08:10.690 --> 08:11.980
No wonder Manager Yu

08:12.370 --> 08:15.430
turned down my request
to book the whole place earlier.

08:15.500 --> 08:17.860
Apparently, my business
wasn't enough to interest you guys.

08:17.860 --> 08:18.660
Alright then.

08:19.450 --> 08:21.100
Let's talk another day.

08:31.910 --> 08:32.620
Where is he?

08:33.659 --> 08:34.330
Gone.

08:34.450 --> 08:35.380
Gone?

08:36.730 --> 08:38.429
He gave up just like that?

08:38.690 --> 08:39.500
Zheng.

08:39.520 --> 08:41.500
My 30 taels were really well spent.

08:51.970 --> 08:53.490
What happened, Master?

08:56.570 --> 08:57.770
You won't believe it—

08:58.300 --> 09:00.140
I just ran into a dead man,

09:00.490 --> 09:03.350
and that woman actually claimed
he was her husband.

09:04.330 --> 09:05.850
Master, you mean...

09:16.300 --> 09:19.060
Marquis of Wu'an, Xie Zheng.

09:20.200 --> 09:21.200
Xie Zheng?

09:22.520 --> 09:23.920
Isn't he dead?

09:27.970 --> 09:30.100
If the Marquis of Wu'an is still alive,

09:30.490 --> 09:33.350
I'm afraid Lord Changxin's plan
won't go smoothly.

09:35.330 --> 09:37.050
That smart father of mine

09:37.210 --> 09:40.640
intended to use the move of bandits
stealing military grain

09:41.020 --> 09:42.400
to drive out refugees and create panic,

09:42.400 --> 09:43.540
and then finish the operation.

09:43.540 --> 09:44.660
But now,

09:45.300 --> 09:46.970
not only is the Marquis of Wu'an not dead,

09:46.970 --> 09:50.030
but he even knows we purchased
200,000 piculs of grain.

09:50.590 --> 09:52.920
Obviously, he's been prepared all along.

09:53.660 --> 09:56.120
It's still hard to say who will win
in the end.

09:56.420 --> 09:59.630
This game is getting
more and more interesting.

10:02.050 --> 10:05.350
Back then, you intentionally
leaked information, Master,

10:05.350 --> 10:06.490
to lead the Marquis of Wu'an
to investigate

10:06.490 --> 10:08.610
the Jinzhou Massacre from 16 years ago

10:08.610 --> 10:11.420
because you believed Prime Minister Wei
wouldn't allow him to reopen the case.

10:11.420 --> 10:12.810
Your plan was to use Prime Minister Wei

10:12.810 --> 10:15.210
to get rid of that serious threat
Xie Zheng.

10:15.570 --> 10:17.660
But now, he's still alive...

10:18.640 --> 10:20.540
Should we reveal his whereabouts

10:20.540 --> 10:21.940
to Wei Yan in secret

10:22.210 --> 10:25.140
and try to get Wei Yan to do
the dirty work for us again?

10:25.210 --> 10:25.810
No.

10:26.330 --> 10:27.810
I tried to turn them against each other
back then

10:27.810 --> 10:29.780
just to sever Wei Yan's support.

10:30.300 --> 10:32.780
The Marquis of Wu'an
has never been our enemy.

10:32.780 --> 10:36.210
Now that the rift between uncle and nephew
is a done deal,

10:36.210 --> 10:38.180
and the Marquis of Wu'an has been
cast out to the countryside,

10:38.180 --> 10:40.640
we can take this opportunity
to win him over.

10:41.850 --> 10:43.570
Take my East Palace seal
and use my former identity

10:43.570 --> 10:46.630
as the Crown Prince of the Eastern Palace
to lure him in.

10:47.570 --> 10:48.210
Got it.

10:51.490 --> 10:53.060
As for Manager Yu...

10:53.540 --> 10:54.330
Her?

10:57.610 --> 10:59.870
Just have someone keep a close eye on her.

11:00.600 --> 11:02.460
[Yixiang Restaurant]

11:01.090 --> 11:02.900
Come on in, ladies. This way.

11:04.780 --> 11:06.110
Please come in, ladies.

11:06.420 --> 11:07.490
Welcome, ladies.

11:19.450 --> 11:20.210
Mrs. Fan.

11:29.450 --> 11:30.140
Changyu.

11:30.780 --> 11:31.380
Come here.

11:34.450 --> 11:35.180
Look.

11:35.900 --> 11:37.140
The restaurant is so lively—

11:37.140 --> 11:38.380
it's all thanks to you.

11:38.380 --> 11:40.070
What do you mean, thanks to me?

11:40.140 --> 11:42.300
Ever since your husband came by,

11:42.300 --> 11:44.560
that Qi fellow hasn't bothered me again.

11:45.090 --> 11:46.810
I can finally focus on
running the business.

11:46.810 --> 11:48.020
Now look—the restaurant is so lively.

11:48.020 --> 11:49.620
Of course it's thanks to you.

11:51.060 --> 11:51.810
Come with me.

11:54.660 --> 11:57.460
I wonder what Chef Li is cooking
for New Year's Eve.

11:57.940 --> 12:00.000
What are you planning to eat tonight?

12:01.450 --> 12:02.690
Cabbage and tofu,

12:03.420 --> 12:04.260
and stir-fried pork.

12:04.260 --> 12:04.940
Go on.

12:07.540 --> 12:09.470
Hello, Mother. Hello, Auntie Fan.

12:10.090 --> 12:10.660
Sit.

12:12.420 --> 12:14.220
What is Changning doing at home?

12:14.260 --> 12:15.300
I miss her.

12:15.690 --> 12:16.900
How about after New Year's Eve,

12:16.900 --> 12:19.500
you come over to our place
and hang out with her?

12:20.930 --> 12:22.440
Mother, can I go?

12:24.570 --> 12:25.410
Fine.

12:25.940 --> 12:26.970
Just this once.

12:28.060 --> 12:29.020
Changning said

12:29.050 --> 12:30.980
she'd show me her family heirloom.

12:31.300 --> 12:33.730
Family heirloom?

12:37.380 --> 12:39.510
She probably meant our butcher knife.

12:39.970 --> 12:41.770
I guess that won't be necessary.

12:42.060 --> 12:43.220
That's so cool!

12:43.240 --> 12:45.100
So it's actually a butcher knife!

12:48.540 --> 12:50.380
I have things to discuss with Auntie Fan.

12:50.380 --> 12:51.440
Go study first.

12:55.900 --> 12:56.540
Let's go.

12:59.660 --> 13:00.490
Qianqian.

13:00.970 --> 13:03.340
Aren't you a bit too strict with Bao'er?

13:04.490 --> 13:05.330
Not at all.

13:05.730 --> 13:07.590
I just want him to succeed in life.

13:10.330 --> 13:11.290
Changyu.

13:11.850 --> 13:13.200
Tomorrow is New Year's Eve,

13:13.200 --> 13:14.990
and you'll surely be swamped.

13:15.690 --> 13:19.140
I want to wish you in advance
a smooth and happy year ahead.

13:19.810 --> 13:21.120
I'm not a child.

13:21.140 --> 13:22.870
Why give me a lucky money pouch?

13:23.660 --> 13:25.060
Us girls

13:25.060 --> 13:26.730
are forever young.

13:26.940 --> 13:28.400
Come on. Let's get a drink.

13:28.940 --> 13:30.450
Drinking at noon?

13:31.210 --> 13:32.940
We women drink when we feel like it,

13:32.940 --> 13:33.940
not when the clock says so.

13:33.940 --> 13:35.300
If not now, then when?

13:37.480 --> 13:41.330
[Overflowing Joy and Good Fortune]

13:42.180 --> 13:43.210
Cheers!

13:47.940 --> 13:48.810
Qianqian.

13:49.450 --> 13:51.780
The last time I was this happy

13:52.330 --> 13:54.900
was the day I married Yan Zheng.

13:58.690 --> 13:59.610
Changyu,

14:00.540 --> 14:03.540
you've been married for
quite some time now.

14:04.380 --> 14:06.120
That husband of yours—

14:06.270 --> 14:07.800
are you satisfied with him?

14:11.450 --> 14:14.140
He's not just all show, is he?

14:14.900 --> 14:16.700
All show?

14:17.610 --> 14:19.850
Yan Zheng is pure gold—

14:20.430 --> 14:22.690
through and through.

14:23.330 --> 14:24.950
He's that good?

14:25.900 --> 14:26.900
I'm going to find someone

14:26.900 --> 14:28.020
to beat Granny Kang up.

14:28.020 --> 14:31.150
She said you two hadn't even
consummated your marriage.

14:31.420 --> 14:33.420
You were talking about
consummating the marriage?

14:33.420 --> 14:34.680
What else would I mean?

14:34.970 --> 14:36.900
Granny Kang really has a potty mouth.

14:36.900 --> 14:38.900
It's fine. I'll beat her up.
I can afford the damages.

14:38.900 --> 14:39.630
Don't worry.

14:39.730 --> 14:40.350
Qianqian.

14:41.690 --> 14:43.300
Actually...

14:44.020 --> 14:46.570
She wasn't entirely wrong.

14:49.090 --> 14:52.140
Which part wasn't wrong?

14:54.260 --> 14:55.610
One day,

14:56.330 --> 15:00.020
Mrs. Zhao locked the two of us in a room.

15:01.330 --> 15:03.570
He probably wanted to kiss me.

15:05.690 --> 15:07.550
Did you eat tangerine peel candy?

15:07.810 --> 15:10.320
You smell like tangerine peel candy.

15:10.850 --> 15:13.610
Do you want some now?

15:18.850 --> 15:19.690
And then?

15:20.450 --> 15:22.050
Then...

15:24.090 --> 15:25.540
We had a fight.

15:31.450 --> 15:33.250
So you two are actually serious?

15:42.140 --> 15:44.210
Actually, I know deep down

15:46.490 --> 15:47.450
that

15:50.210 --> 15:51.850
he'd leave sooner or later.

15:55.970 --> 15:58.660
I've hinted at it several times,

16:02.380 --> 16:04.440
yet he never gave a different answer.

16:12.020 --> 16:14.090
Your man does seem to be

16:15.060 --> 16:16.940
too big a fish for your small pond.

16:20.690 --> 16:21.380
It's okay.

16:21.940 --> 16:23.340
If he insists on leaving,

16:23.690 --> 16:26.450
just have a baby with him before he goes.

16:26.970 --> 16:27.850
Think about it—

16:28.020 --> 16:30.180
if the child turns out
as good-looking as him,

16:30.180 --> 16:32.180
that would be a kind of blessing too.

16:34.970 --> 16:37.420
That won't do, right?

16:38.780 --> 16:41.710
Wouldn't that basically be
taking advantage of him?

16:42.020 --> 16:44.300
You know the saying, "you can't catch a wolf
without sacrificing a lamb."

16:44.300 --> 16:45.450
Wait—actually, in this case it's:

16:45.450 --> 16:48.180
you won't get a baby
without feeding the wolf.

16:52.810 --> 16:53.540
Don't worry.

16:53.970 --> 16:56.020
Leave this to me.

17:05.810 --> 17:10.240
[Xigu Lane]

17:18.859 --> 17:22.490
Zhao Xun, the shopkeeper of
Lin'an Rice Shop, is here to visit.

17:26.050 --> 17:27.369
It's freezing cold.

17:27.420 --> 17:29.550
Won't Your Lordship invite me in?

17:39.380 --> 17:40.240
Your Lordship.

17:41.100 --> 17:41.960
Your Lordship?

17:42.800 --> 17:51.730
[Fill Your Belly]

17:50.770 --> 17:52.170
How did you recognize me?

17:53.250 --> 17:55.770
I used to do business
in Jizhou and Yanzhou.

17:56.290 --> 17:59.150
I was lucky enough to
have seen Your Lordship there.

18:02.140 --> 18:02.970
So?

18:04.210 --> 18:06.340
Why are you here today?

18:10.100 --> 18:12.240
Your Xie family has always been
loyal and virtuous,

18:12.240 --> 18:15.100
which is a fact
known throughout the whole country.

18:15.180 --> 18:16.650
Yet Heaven is unjust,

18:16.970 --> 18:19.100
allowing evildoers to bring you harm.

18:19.660 --> 18:22.460
I too feel indignation
on Your Lordship's behalf.

18:25.490 --> 18:27.350
I don't understand what you mean.

18:28.000 --> 18:30.860
Wasn't the reason Wei Yan
hunted Your Lordship down

18:30.860 --> 18:32.030
because you were investigating

18:32.030 --> 18:34.230
the Jinzhou Massacre from 16 years ago?

18:41.100 --> 18:42.580
Who exactly are you?

18:58.540 --> 19:00.630
[Chengde Heavenly Treasure]

19:00.940 --> 19:02.220
Sixteen years ago,

19:03.100 --> 19:05.030
in that fire at the Eastern Palace—

19:05.620 --> 19:07.420
I was one of the lucky survivors.

19:09.420 --> 19:11.580
Wei Yan is a treacherous official
in power,

19:11.580 --> 19:13.240
supporting a puppet emperor.

19:13.450 --> 19:14.710
We are a group of people

19:15.140 --> 19:16.900
who want to restore order.

19:18.770 --> 19:19.730
So,

19:20.770 --> 19:21.990
do you have any proof?

19:23.380 --> 19:26.560
Crown Prince Chengde
and Your Lordship's father

19:26.820 --> 19:28.680
both died tragically in Jinzhou.

19:29.660 --> 19:31.250
Then the Emperor abdicated,

19:31.250 --> 19:33.100
and the Eastern Palace caught fire.

19:33.100 --> 19:35.760
All these suspicious events
pointed to Wei Yan.

19:35.970 --> 19:38.340
Your Lordship's father and the Crown Prince
both died in battle,

19:38.340 --> 19:42.050
and their bodies were hung on the city wall
by the Beijue people for 3 days.

19:42.050 --> 19:45.050
Doesn't Your Lordship want to
avenge this blood feud?

19:49.140 --> 19:52.420
Your Lordship had just started
reinvestigating the Jinzhou Massacre,

19:52.420 --> 19:53.860
and you immediately got hunted down

19:53.860 --> 19:55.140
and ended up here—

19:55.530 --> 19:57.140
isn't that proof enough?

20:06.730 --> 20:07.410
Not enough.

20:18.380 --> 20:19.580
We also found out that

20:20.250 --> 20:21.970
Wei Yan sent his Suicide Warriors

20:21.970 --> 20:23.970
across the Capital and 17 prefectures

20:23.970 --> 20:25.230
to kill over 10 people—

20:26.530 --> 20:28.790
all retainers who once worked for Wei Yan

20:29.210 --> 20:30.650
and later retired.

20:30.730 --> 20:32.820
What exactly does the Fan family have

20:32.820 --> 20:35.820
that's worth the Wei family's
Iron Suicide Warriors coming here for?

20:35.820 --> 20:37.280
It was the Prime Minister.

20:37.450 --> 20:39.180
He sent me here to find a letter.

20:40.380 --> 20:43.310
So Fan Erniu must have also
worked for Wei Yan before,

20:43.780 --> 20:45.910
which is why he kept being hunted down.

20:46.900 --> 20:47.760
Your Lordship.

20:48.490 --> 20:50.370
Wei Yan is immensely powerful now,

20:50.370 --> 20:52.620
with ambitions that could
overshadow the heavens.

20:52.620 --> 20:53.940
To bring him down,

20:54.380 --> 20:56.380
doesn't Your Lordship need an ally?

20:57.140 --> 20:58.770
How can I trust you?

20:59.180 --> 21:00.910
How can Your Lordship trust me?

21:03.450 --> 21:04.780
Give me a deposit first.

21:05.420 --> 21:06.420
What deposit?

21:08.580 --> 21:10.050
200,000 piculs of grain—

21:11.140 --> 21:12.270
how does that sound?

21:15.770 --> 21:18.010
It seems he really knows about

21:18.010 --> 21:21.270
my grain collection from all across
Jizhou and Chongzhou.

21:22.340 --> 21:24.050
We bought from many sources,

21:24.450 --> 21:26.710
with over 100 grain merchants involved.

21:26.820 --> 21:28.860
How did he know so accurately?

21:29.210 --> 21:32.690
I'd actually like to ask you that.

21:34.100 --> 21:36.430
Forgive me, Master. It was my negligence.

21:38.730 --> 21:40.900
But it's good that
he's willing to name his terms.

21:40.900 --> 21:42.360
It's business, after all.

21:43.340 --> 21:45.450
Once he quotes a price, we can talk.

21:48.860 --> 21:50.210
200,000 piculs...

21:50.770 --> 21:51.530
Master,

21:51.770 --> 21:53.680
the grain from all across
Chongzhou and Jizhou

21:53.680 --> 21:55.730
has almost been emptied by us
these past months.

21:55.730 --> 21:58.260
He didn't ask you to give it
all at once, did he?

22:00.450 --> 22:02.940
Father never cared about me,

22:03.180 --> 22:06.050
and the position of Crown Prince
was meant for Sui Yuanqing.

22:06.050 --> 22:08.980
But if we can gain the support of
the Marquis of Wu'an,

22:09.940 --> 22:11.800
our chances of success will soar.

22:12.250 --> 22:13.780
What if the Marquis of Wu'an

22:13.810 --> 22:15.590
doesn't believe your identity,

22:15.590 --> 22:17.420
takes the grain, and turns against us,
Master?

22:17.420 --> 22:18.380
What then?

22:18.660 --> 22:19.590
Turn against us?

22:20.140 --> 22:21.530
Who else can he turn to?

22:22.210 --> 22:24.540
Can he possibly go back to
work for Wei Yan?

22:25.490 --> 22:28.140
As long as he's willing to help me
wholeheartedly,

22:28.140 --> 22:29.860
let alone 200,000 piculs of grain—

22:29.860 --> 22:31.290
I can even grant all 4 prefectures

22:31.290 --> 22:33.220
of the Northwest to him as his fief.

22:33.380 --> 22:34.110
Understood.

22:34.530 --> 22:36.060
I'll see to it immediately.

22:46.140 --> 22:48.010
Wei Yan, oh Wei Yan.

22:49.820 --> 22:51.140
You will soon

22:51.140 --> 22:53.820
be bitten by the ungrateful wolf

22:54.770 --> 22:56.120
you raised yourself.

22:59.940 --> 23:00.870
Prime Minister.

23:01.900 --> 23:05.430
I was investigating
Grand Tutor Li's dealings with the rebels,

23:05.730 --> 23:06.860
and I accidentally found out
that when the Marquis of Wu'an

23:06.860 --> 23:10.060
was reinvestigating the Jinzhou cases
from 16 years ago,

23:10.340 --> 23:13.870
it was exactly Lord Changxin's people
who plotted against him.

23:17.180 --> 23:19.970
If Xie Zheng didn't exist in this world,

23:20.970 --> 23:24.700
Lord Changxin would have
one less major threat on the battlefield.

23:26.210 --> 23:28.210
The Sui family is

23:29.050 --> 23:31.210
trying to ruin my great plans.

23:35.100 --> 23:36.210
There's one more thing.

23:36.210 --> 23:38.100
Li Huai'an was recalled to the Capital
by Grand Tutor Li

23:38.100 --> 23:39.500
for some unknown reason.

23:41.180 --> 23:42.820
With Princess Royal back in the Capital,

23:42.820 --> 23:45.620
that old coot probably wants to
push the marriage,

23:46.340 --> 23:49.470
so he hurried to
recall his eldest legitimate grandson.

23:51.050 --> 23:52.140
Just leave him be.

23:53.380 --> 23:55.690
Write to He Jingyuan immediately

23:56.010 --> 23:57.860
and tell him to defend Lucheng
to the death.

23:57.860 --> 24:00.190
That's the place for the decisive battle.

24:01.710 --> 24:05.460
[New Year's Eve]

24:14.180 --> 24:15.460
Happy New Year.

24:15.490 --> 24:16.820
Come on, everyone, time for dinner.

24:16.820 --> 24:18.110
Coming. Coming.

24:18.380 --> 24:19.840
Happy New Year, Mrs. Wang.

24:23.730 --> 24:24.970
Happy New Year, Mrs. San.

24:24.970 --> 24:26.210
Happy New Year, Mr. San.

24:26.210 --> 24:27.450
Happy New Year.

24:27.850 --> 24:30.890
[Chunfeng Tofu Shop]

24:28.490 --> 24:29.730
Happy New Year to you.

24:32.970 --> 24:34.570
Keep writing. Keep writing.

24:35.010 --> 24:35.740
Horizontal.

24:37.010 --> 24:38.340
Horizontal, vertical.

24:39.530 --> 24:40.140
Vertical.

24:41.660 --> 24:45.210
Horizontal with a turn,
left-falling, right-falling.

24:52.050 --> 24:54.620
Sister, Zheng is teaching me how to write.

24:54.940 --> 24:55.660
Good girl.

25:00.970 --> 25:03.770
Do you know how to write
Spring Festival couplets?

25:05.860 --> 25:09.290
My mother used to write them every year.

25:09.690 --> 25:12.350
Can you write Spring Festival couplets,
Zheng?

25:12.380 --> 25:13.380
Get me the paper.

25:13.860 --> 25:14.490
Okay.

25:29.860 --> 25:31.190
You ground too much ink.

25:33.680 --> 25:35.910
♪ The scenery is as clear as me ♪

25:33.970 --> 25:35.500
Then write a few more pairs.

25:35.660 --> 25:37.290
We can give some to Mrs. Zhao
and the others,

25:36.950 --> 25:38.170
♪ With very pale colors ♪

25:38.050 --> 25:40.460
and we can put the rest on the doorframes
of all these rooms.

25:38.950 --> 25:41.910
♪ Just like the outline in the mirror ♪

25:40.690 --> 25:41.490
For good omen.

25:42.370 --> 25:44.860
♪ I think that's me, being naive ♪

25:43.140 --> 25:43.690
Alright.

25:45.610 --> 25:47.090
♪ Unlocking my heart ♪

25:47.770 --> 25:51.930
♪ I hid you in my soul ♪

25:55.380 --> 25:57.940
♪ The moon is as quiet as me ♪

25:58.650 --> 26:00.260
♪ The light shines ♪

26:00.970 --> 26:03.670
♪ It illuminates
the turbulence in my heart ♪

26:03.010 --> 26:05.160
[Sprouting Grass]

26:04.140 --> 26:06.750
♪ It seems to be the fire of love ♪

26:07.370 --> 26:09.110
♪ Just a few sparks ♪

26:09.560 --> 26:14.470
♪ Let me hide in your heart ♪

26:16.880 --> 26:18.040
♪ I pray that our love ♪

26:18.070 --> 26:20.760
♪ Will never end ♪

26:21.430 --> 26:22.400
♪ It's worth my foolishly waiting ♪

26:22.430 --> 26:24.690
♪ For a lifetime ♪

26:25.330 --> 26:29.380
♪ Clear and quiet as me ♪

26:26.580 --> 26:28.660
D-Did I accidentally touch you?

26:29.420 --> 26:31.380
It's fine. I just got a bit too much ink
on the brush.

26:29.790 --> 26:33.490
♪ So what if we encounter difficulties? ♪

26:34.280 --> 26:35.210
♪ I pray that our love
will not be like sand ♪

26:35.230 --> 26:37.740
♪ Slipping into the sea ♪

26:37.260 --> 26:46.350
[Be a Good Person]

26:39.020 --> 26:39.960
♪ I'd rather use this life ♪

26:39.490 --> 26:40.900
Your calligraphy is really good.

26:39.980 --> 26:42.330
♪ To guard our love forever ♪

26:43.130 --> 26:47.020
♪ Clear and quiet as me ♪

26:45.210 --> 26:46.290
What a pity.

26:47.340 --> 26:48.210
But it's okay.

26:47.500 --> 26:58.140
♪ Why do we need
to seek cause and effect ♪

26:49.600 --> 26:54.030
[As ice thaws, the springs awaken]
[With snow gone, new grass sprouts]

26:49.690 --> 26:53.090
I'll just put this pair
on the door of Changning's and my room.

26:53.290 --> 26:55.340
Ice something...

26:56.290 --> 26:58.090
Spring something something...

26:59.420 --> 27:03.730
Snow something... New grass sprouts.

27:04.490 --> 27:06.250
As ice thaws, the springs awaken.

27:06.250 --> 27:08.180
With snow gone, new grass sprouts.

27:09.580 --> 27:12.970
When my mother wrote
Spring Festival couplets,

27:13.140 --> 27:14.360
she didn't like writing those

27:14.360 --> 27:16.420
clichéd auspicious phrases either.

27:16.860 --> 27:17.860
Do you like these?

27:20.890 --> 27:24.510
[Be a Good Person]

27:43.380 --> 27:44.580
You know how to paint?

27:46.970 --> 27:47.860
Only a little.

27:55.050 --> 27:56.010
That's enough.

27:58.970 --> 28:01.050
If you go and sell
your calligraphy and paintings out there,

28:01.050 --> 28:03.180
you'll definitely make a lot of money.

28:07.010 --> 28:09.070
I don't paint what doesn't please me.

28:12.140 --> 28:13.940
I want to write something too.

28:16.170 --> 28:17.500
Write a top scroll then.

28:19.420 --> 28:21.620
Come on, Changning,
write a top scroll.

28:23.820 --> 28:25.080
What should you write?

28:26.140 --> 28:27.380
What should I write?

28:38.970 --> 28:40.250
Just write this.

28:46.480 --> 28:50.430
[You'll Be Rich]

28:48.730 --> 28:49.990
How's this top scroll?

28:53.450 --> 28:54.580
Just like...

28:55.860 --> 28:57.460
Joining a dog's tail to sable fur.

28:57.460 --> 29:01.880
[You'll Be Rich]

29:00.430 --> 29:02.290
That means it's very good, right?

29:06.730 --> 29:08.590
That means it's very good, right?

29:10.600 --> 29:11.750
It's perfect.

29:12.650 --> 29:15.710
[You'll Be Rich]

29:16.380 --> 29:18.030
I wrote it too well.

29:18.380 --> 29:19.530
I'm amazing.

29:21.770 --> 29:23.770
Oh right, we're missing the falcon.

29:29.450 --> 29:30.500
Good falcon,

29:30.860 --> 29:33.060
let's celebrate the New Year together.

29:37.690 --> 29:39.490
With the falcon's claw print,

29:39.660 --> 29:42.390
our family is complete.

29:45.790 --> 29:48.350
[You'll Be Rich]

29:46.530 --> 29:47.210
Look.

29:50.450 --> 29:51.380
Dear.

29:51.730 --> 29:53.170
Lower. Lower.

29:54.050 --> 29:54.970
Alright, alright. Right there.

29:54.970 --> 29:56.490
Don't move. Don't move further. That's it.

29:56.490 --> 29:58.620
-Alright.
-Let's go check on Changyu.

30:00.100 --> 30:00.820
Okay.

30:03.210 --> 30:03.970
Dear.

30:04.660 --> 30:05.940
How is the calligraphy?

30:05.940 --> 30:07.350
It's beautiful.

30:07.370 --> 30:09.860
-I've never seen such nice calligraphy before.
-He wrote this, right?

30:09.860 --> 30:12.940
-I guess so.
-You're illiterate. Can you really understand it?

30:12.940 --> 30:14.250
I may not be able to read,

30:14.250 --> 30:16.470
but I can tell this calligraphy
is valuable.

30:16.470 --> 30:17.940
Look how square and upright
the characters are.

30:17.940 --> 30:18.860
So neat and proper.

30:18.860 --> 30:20.790
It's obvious it's worth a fortune.

30:21.400 --> 30:23.180
Mr. Zhao, Mrs. Zhao.

30:23.450 --> 30:25.340
The couplets are written so well.

30:25.580 --> 30:26.530
Who wrote these?

30:26.530 --> 30:28.990
Changyu's husband wrote all of these.

30:32.580 --> 30:33.710
Changyu's husband.

30:35.900 --> 30:36.730
Changyu,

30:37.580 --> 30:40.350
your husband writes really nice couplets—

30:40.450 --> 30:43.090
even better than the ones Scholar Song

30:43.120 --> 30:44.490
wrote in previous years.

30:44.490 --> 30:45.660
That's why I say

30:45.660 --> 30:47.620
our Changyu has good taste.

30:48.530 --> 30:50.380
Can he write a pair for me too?

30:52.860 --> 30:55.010
-Yeah. Write a pair for us too.
-Write for all of us.

30:55.010 --> 30:55.770
Sis.

30:56.100 --> 30:56.860
I'm sorry.

30:56.860 --> 30:59.060
We ran out of red paper for the couplets.

30:59.450 --> 31:00.860
Oh, red paper for the couplets?

31:00.860 --> 31:03.820
I've got plenty of red paper at home
from previous years.

31:03.820 --> 31:05.490
I've got some at home too.

31:05.490 --> 31:06.900
-I have some too.
-Me too.

31:07.140 --> 31:07.770
Alright.

31:08.900 --> 31:10.100
Bring the paper over.

31:10.580 --> 31:11.140
Alright!

31:11.480 --> 31:12.860
Quick, go get the red paper.

31:12.860 --> 31:13.820
Okay, thanks.

31:13.820 --> 31:15.100
See you in a bit.

31:15.530 --> 31:16.290
Let's go.

31:25.860 --> 31:27.140
If you aren't willing,

31:27.140 --> 31:28.450
you didn't have to agree.

31:28.450 --> 31:29.650
Don't worry about me.

31:30.620 --> 31:31.490
I am willing.

31:33.660 --> 31:35.290
You just said

31:35.290 --> 31:37.690
you wouldn't paint what didn't please you.

31:40.450 --> 31:41.920
Now it pleases you?

31:42.420 --> 31:43.220
Grind the ink.

31:44.010 --> 31:44.660
Changyu.

31:45.690 --> 31:46.660
Mrs. Zhuang.

31:46.660 --> 31:48.450
Here's some homemade puffed rice candy—

31:48.450 --> 31:50.110
a little snack for Changning.

31:51.010 --> 31:51.680
But...

31:51.820 --> 31:52.490
Take it.

31:52.490 --> 31:55.420
Changyu, I heard your husband
was writing Spring Festival couplets for people.

31:55.420 --> 31:58.010
Our family hasn't gotten ours written yet,
either,

31:58.010 --> 32:00.260
so I boldly came along.

32:00.860 --> 32:02.700
It's nothing fancy,

32:03.050 --> 32:06.140
just some freshly ground tofu
for you to taste.

32:08.250 --> 32:08.970
Ladies,

32:09.340 --> 32:10.290
please have a seat first.

32:10.290 --> 32:11.350
Alright, alright.

32:13.050 --> 32:13.580
Thank you.

32:13.580 --> 32:14.380
Here's the red paper I brought.

32:14.380 --> 32:15.510
Alright, thank you.

32:37.250 --> 32:40.010
Harmony brings peace to all frontiers.

32:40.460 --> 32:41.390
Done.

32:42.010 --> 32:42.870
It's finished.

32:45.250 --> 32:47.210
"Lanterns shine on homes to celebrate
the prosperous year."

32:47.210 --> 32:50.180
"The ox carries spring to plow
the green fields."

32:50.180 --> 32:52.100
It means that when spring comes
next year,

32:52.100 --> 32:53.490
there will be a bumper harvest,

32:53.490 --> 32:56.090
and the whole family
will be happy and healthy.

33:03.860 --> 33:05.100
Though storm and darkness fill the sky

33:05.100 --> 33:06.970
and the rooster crows without end,

33:06.970 --> 33:08.290
now that I have met you—

33:08.380 --> 33:10.110
how could my heart not rejoice?

33:10.660 --> 33:11.770
The meaning of this poem line is that

33:11.770 --> 33:14.670
amidst the gloom and pouring rain,

33:14.770 --> 33:16.340
the roosters crow in panic.

33:17.420 --> 33:19.900
Yet, precisely in this chaotic moment,

33:21.180 --> 33:22.400
I glance around,

33:23.490 --> 33:24.850
and I catch sight of her.

33:25.940 --> 33:28.450
It's like parting the clouds and mist,

33:28.580 --> 33:30.970
and a beam of light falls upon me—

33:32.940 --> 33:34.410
warm and radiant,

33:35.140 --> 33:36.670
filling my heart with joy.

33:37.860 --> 33:40.050
When I heard him recite this line before,

33:40.050 --> 33:41.780
I just thought it sounded nice,

33:41.970 --> 33:44.230
but I had no idea
what was so good about it.

33:45.180 --> 33:46.560
Until just now,

33:47.730 --> 33:49.930
when he turned his head and looked at me.

33:51.970 --> 33:53.100
In that instant,

33:53.580 --> 33:55.780
the courtyard fell completely silent.

33:56.820 --> 34:00.600
Even the falling snow seemed lighter,

34:02.010 --> 34:03.700
and even the wind blowing over

34:03.860 --> 34:06.290
felt softer and gentler.

34:07.530 --> 34:09.570
It was like the sun
on the Winter Solstice—

34:09.570 --> 34:11.230
neither slanting nor skewed,

34:11.780 --> 34:15.050
shining perfectly on me.

34:16.010 --> 34:18.070
It turns out when you are truly happy,

34:18.260 --> 34:19.900
your heart sings.

34:20.739 --> 34:23.199
Just like when you sit by the stove,

34:23.570 --> 34:25.530
and the firewood crackles softly,

34:26.219 --> 34:29.219
crisp and warm.

34:36.610 --> 34:38.139
Your hand must hurt, right?

34:38.699 --> 34:39.500
It's nothing.

34:40.090 --> 34:41.350
Still toughing it out.

35:01.610 --> 35:03.270
Are you here for couplets too?

35:06.700 --> 35:07.780
Before...

35:08.860 --> 35:12.490
Before, it was always my elder grandson,
Kang Dan, who wrote the Spring Festival couplets.

35:12.490 --> 35:14.220
But later, he got into trouble

35:14.220 --> 35:16.080
and was sent off for forced labor.

35:16.570 --> 35:17.490
After that,

35:18.260 --> 35:20.130
Scholar Song helped out.

35:21.740 --> 35:24.650
You see, Kang Dan turned 18 this year.

35:24.860 --> 35:26.700
He's timid and simple-minded.

35:27.490 --> 35:28.420
I just hope

35:28.420 --> 35:30.340
that my younger grandson, Xiaohu,

35:30.340 --> 35:33.450
could be smarter and sharper
than his older brother.

35:35.570 --> 35:36.380
You know,

35:37.170 --> 35:38.820
by the end of the year,

35:38.970 --> 35:42.630
isn't life really just about
having something to look forward to?

35:47.650 --> 35:49.820
Next year, or the year after—

35:50.170 --> 35:51.010
perhaps

35:51.610 --> 35:52.940
things will get better.

36:04.050 --> 36:04.710
Please sit.

36:10.780 --> 36:12.380
What do you want me to write?

36:15.500 --> 36:17.740
Just no more wars,

36:18.420 --> 36:19.860
so that our Kang family

36:20.090 --> 36:21.490
could continue our line.

36:23.570 --> 36:25.100
And I hope my two grandsons,

36:26.050 --> 36:28.250
without their parents to protect them,

36:28.610 --> 36:30.540
could still grow up safe and sound.

36:40.260 --> 36:40.900
Okay.

36:50.790 --> 36:51.790
[Composed]

37:08.390 --> 37:12.070
[Ornamented Beauty]

37:16.570 --> 37:17.820
Greetings, Mother.

37:19.150 --> 37:20.860
May I ask why

37:20.970 --> 37:22.630
you summoned me here, Mother?

37:25.970 --> 37:28.570
It's New Year's Eve,
a time for family reunion.

37:28.650 --> 37:30.580
Do I really need a reason

37:30.700 --> 37:32.340
just to see you?

37:33.570 --> 37:34.970
That's not what I meant.

37:42.090 --> 37:45.220
I wish you a prosperous New Year, Mother.

37:45.380 --> 37:47.900
May peace and health be with you always.

37:52.860 --> 37:55.920
You were betrothed to
the Marquis of Wu'an since birth.

37:56.090 --> 37:58.420
Back when the Marquis of Wu'an
was still around,

37:58.420 --> 38:01.050
he was a heroic young man
with great military merits.

38:01.050 --> 38:03.910
Such a fine man would have been
a great match for you,

38:04.300 --> 38:06.900
yet you said you only saw him
as an older brother

38:06.900 --> 38:09.500
and refused to take him as
your Prince Consort.

38:10.010 --> 38:12.130
And now, this failed scheme

38:12.360 --> 38:13.740
has consumed you.

38:15.700 --> 38:17.500
What do you mean by that, Mother?

38:17.650 --> 38:19.530
Ever since you returned to the palace,

38:19.530 --> 38:22.860
you've used illness as an excuse
multiple times to put off meeting Li Huai'an.

38:22.860 --> 38:24.610
I have already made arrangements.

38:24.610 --> 38:28.050
You will go to the Lantern Festival
with him on the fifteenth.

38:29.090 --> 38:30.090
Mother!

38:31.280 --> 38:35.170
The Gongsun family has been barred from
holding office in the court for generations.

38:35.170 --> 38:36.570
This is an imperial regulation

38:36.570 --> 38:37.970
and must never be defied.

38:37.970 --> 38:39.230
As the Princess Royal,

38:39.380 --> 38:41.020
you must not let that scheme

38:41.130 --> 38:43.590
ruin the grand cause of
our imperial family.

38:47.090 --> 38:48.940
I'm not your pawn, Mother.

38:49.470 --> 38:52.260
And I refuse to be manipulated
in this palace scheme.

38:52.260 --> 38:54.340
You only care about family glory

38:54.340 --> 38:55.490
and imperial regulations, Mother.

38:55.490 --> 38:58.550
Have you ever truly cared about
my happiness or sorrow?

38:59.300 --> 39:00.500
In short, from now on,

39:00.700 --> 39:03.700
you must not see anyone
from the Gongsun family again.

39:04.650 --> 39:06.310
Just cut that thought off now.

39:10.700 --> 39:12.560
If there's nothing else, Mother,

39:12.820 --> 39:14.090
I shall take my leave.

39:17.170 --> 39:18.130
Shu!

39:19.090 --> 39:20.650
Your Highness, where are you going?

39:19.180 --> 39:22.010
[Ornamented Beauty]

39:22.260 --> 39:23.660
I'm going to hang myself.

39:23.700 --> 39:25.300
Do you want to join me, Nanny?

39:27.920 --> 39:31.290
[Composed]

39:36.010 --> 39:39.650
Though loved for its clever words,

39:41.610 --> 39:45.260
the bird yearns to fly free.

40:00.380 --> 40:01.860
Come on.

40:02.780 --> 40:03.860
Let's eat.

40:03.860 --> 40:04.890
It smells so good.

40:04.910 --> 40:05.780
Smells so good.

40:05.780 --> 40:07.170
Thank you. Thank you.

40:07.740 --> 40:08.740
Here.

40:09.610 --> 40:10.300
Yummy, yummy.

40:10.300 --> 40:10.940
Yummy.

40:12.190 --> 40:12.650
Eat up.

40:12.650 --> 40:13.380
It's so good.

40:13.700 --> 40:14.710
Coming up.

40:17.230 --> 40:19.380
-Happy New Year!
-Happy New Year!

40:33.570 --> 40:34.530
Let's have another cup.

40:34.530 --> 40:35.260
Fill it up.

40:35.610 --> 40:36.340
Fill it up.

40:37.220 --> 40:38.080
I want some too.

40:38.940 --> 40:41.050
No, you're still injured.

40:41.740 --> 40:43.400
This light liquor won't hurt.

40:43.570 --> 40:44.610
Have some tea instead.

40:44.610 --> 40:45.650
The doctor said

40:45.650 --> 40:47.490
no alcohol until you recover.

40:47.780 --> 40:49.140
I want some too.

40:49.820 --> 40:51.490
Changning, you can't drink either.

40:51.490 --> 40:53.570
Come on, have tea with Zheng.

40:59.490 --> 41:01.820
Eat and drink well. Peace year after year.

41:01.820 --> 41:03.170
Cheers.

41:03.530 --> 41:04.380
Come on.

41:16.700 --> 41:17.520
Yan Zheng.

41:19.490 --> 41:20.570
Why don't we...

41:23.260 --> 41:24.530
Fireworks!

41:29.440 --> 41:30.380
Let's go watch the fireworks.

41:30.380 --> 41:32.510
Come on, let's go watch the fireworks.

41:35.780 --> 41:37.110
Be careful, Changning.

41:38.300 --> 41:39.160
What did you just say?

41:39.160 --> 41:40.290
I didn't catch that.

41:46.650 --> 41:48.510
I... I said I wanted to drink more.

41:51.830 --> 41:55.090
-Come on, let's go upstairs.
-Let's go upstairs and watch.

41:55.650 --> 41:56.300
Good wine.

41:56.970 --> 41:58.170
Don't drink too much.

41:58.530 --> 41:59.820
I'm perfectly sober.

41:59.820 --> 42:01.480
This wine isn't strong at all.

42:04.220 --> 42:05.480
I'll pour you some tea.

42:06.450 --> 42:07.710
Sober up with some tea.

42:15.700 --> 42:17.140
Looking down on me, huh?

42:21.050 --> 42:22.740
My father can drink
a whole jar of strong liquor,

42:22.740 --> 42:24.600
so I can handle at least half a jar.

42:36.650 --> 42:38.260
This wine isn't intoxicating at all.

42:38.260 --> 42:39.940
Come on, bottoms up.

42:42.010 --> 42:42.570
Come on.

42:48.450 --> 42:49.970
You really are drunk.

42:52.420 --> 42:54.090
I'm totally fine.

42:56.260 --> 42:57.490
Happy New Year.

42:57.970 --> 42:59.050
Happy New Year.

43:13.220 --> 43:15.130
You won't get a baby

43:15.610 --> 43:17.370
without feeding the wolf.

43:19.780 --> 43:20.530
What baby?
